external target for the metal work. tools/llama.cpp/build-metal (same pinned
commit 0bb2919, GGML_METAL=ON), llama-bench -ngl 99, M3 Max.

  qwen2.5-0.5b               pp512 tok/s    tg128 tok/s
  q8_0                        10570          245.8
  f16                         10949          188.3

engine at M1 for scale: q8_0 decode 26.4 gpu, 84.3 cpu threaded.
